{"tid":2161203,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】港泰死者女兒投訴檢疫營兩人一房 或致父親感染 社署：床與床保持 1.5 米距離","createTime":"2020-08-17T12:11:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T12:36:30.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ef2045d3c5fb1a7a71aca678f3c1862a68a3624b","tid":2161203,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T12:11:39.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情至今，已有 69 人因染病死亡，當中絕大部分是長者。《立場》早前訪問一位港泰院友死者女兒，她質疑政府在處理院舍長者撤離一事上安排失當，長者要 2 人共住一間房，認為父親可能是因此感染。負責相關檢疫中心的社會福利署回覆查詢，承認會按需要安排多於一人在同一房間，但強調會保持最少 1.5 米距離，以及保持清潔。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%B8%AF%E6%B3%B0%E6%AD%BB%E8%80%85%E5%A5%B3%E5%85%92%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E6%AA%A2%E7%96%AB%E7%87%9F%E5%85%A9%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%80%E6%88%BF-%E6%88%96%E8%87%B4%E7%88%B6%E8%A6%AA%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93-%E7%A4%BE%E7%BD%B2-%E5%BA%8A%E8%88%87%E5%BA%8A%E4%BF%9D%E6%8C%81-1-5-%E7%B1%B3%E8%B7%9D%E9%9B%A2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%2585%2592%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E7%2596%25AB%25E7%2587%259F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2588%25BF-%25E6%2588%2596%25E8%2587%25B4%25E7%2588%25B6%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E6%2584%259F%25E6%259F%2593-%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E7%25BD%25B2-%25E5%25BA%258A%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25BA%258A%25E4%25BF%259D%25E6%258C%2581-1-5-%25E7%25B1%25B3%25E8%25B7%259D%25E9%259B%25A2%2F&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21Bzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=7a23b171\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%2585%2592%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E7%2596%25AB%25E7%2587%259F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2588%25BF-